{"tid":2026633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店唔係善堂，唔係老馮請你返去hea","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:12:00.000Z","uid":48234,"like":62,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6e48100458e43629d3943ad30c76c0c13197be","tid":2026633,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"去打工，就係出賣勞力獲得報酬<br />\n有啲係唔駛用腦做重複動作<br />\n有啲係用腦諗清楚先唔會錯<br />\n係手足嘅，打黃店工嘅，唔該記住<br />\n黃店係要全力支持<br />\n幫襯黃店係其一方法<br />\n打工交足貨甚至超額完成都係一種方法<br />\n<br />\n順便一提，老鳳鼓勵黃店唔好俾固定人工手足<br />\n用底薪花紅制度，評級制度去鼓勵手足努力打好份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7590a2e957fb7427c4184e7140390c9bd76ec2","tid":2026633,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"全力支持手足，但亦都請手足互相全力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae84c9f6bd0c909f677a1be39d462aa27f16b8e","tid":2026633,"uid":69472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"做好啲唔好做臭手足個朵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阻阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入嚟幫下手足 或者推下po<br />\n<br />\n［召喚寫信師］荔枝角在囚手足有事請大家幫忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026624</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1f9d1507b2a5a9ca2d8507fc8955a34509b8f09","tid":2026633,"uid":265839,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"黃店可以輕手啲, 唔使下下公開處刑<br />\n<br />\n手足請自重, 工作態度要認真, 呢啲基本做人態度"},{"pid":"01e3077c2650a10e5c01eb9962ca03c3130da4d1","tid":2026633,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f9d1507b2a5a9ca2d8507fc8955a34509b8f09","tid":2026633,"uid":265839,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"黃店可以輕手啲, 唔使下下公開處刑<br />\n<br />\n手足請自重, 工作態度要認真, 呢啲基本做人態度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":